      "content": "i know i should talk to my doctor but i can't get an appointment for like two weeks and i am exhausted. it's just melatonin, right? it's just a natural supplement. it shouldn't really do anything crazy with a prescription pill, surely it's fine to just take them together to make sure i actually stay asleep? i'm just looking for a bit of reassurance that it's not super dangerous.",
